## PL Direct Book helpers — review-friendly naming

Scope: `resources/js/services/property_liability/burglary/` + Burglary Vue (7 products: 0189, 0191–0196).

### 1. Names = 1–2 words

| Kind | Pattern | Good | Bad |
|------|---------|------|-----|
| File | noun or adj+noun | `on.js`, `tab1.js`, `plan-mid.js` | `direct-book-quotation-tab1-validation.js` |
| Fn / var | verb+noun / adj+noun | `fillPlan`, `checkTab1`, `saleChannel` | `hydrateDirectBookPlanFields` |
| Const | SHORT_CAPS OK | `QUOTE_CODES` | `DIRECT_BOOK_QUOTE_ROLLOUT_CODES` |

Prefer **one word** when clear (`on`, `mid`, `err`, `docs`).

**Readable short > cryptic short.** Match Laravel `Str` / Vue feel:

| Good | Bad (too cryptic) |
|------|-------------------|
| `normalizeErr`, `dropdownVal`, `sumInsuredProps` | `normErr`, `ddValue`, `siProps` |
| `makeMidHandlers`, `stripMidFields` | `midHandlers`, `stripMid` |
| `syncEndorsements`, `clearPlanPick` | `syncEnds`, `clearPick` |

Full quality scorecard: `06-pl-quality-bar.mdc`.

### 2. Folder map

```
burglary/
  on.js          # rollout / shell gate
  tab1.js        # Tab1 hydrate / map
  tab1-check.js  # Tab1 validate / prefill
  plan.js        # plan hydrate
  plan-mid.js    # plan intermediary grid
  mid.js         # business / rates / plan pick
  clause.js      # clause multiselect
  limits.js      # premium / rows / merge tabs
  docs.js        # payloads / attachments
  err.js         # API errors
  policy/
    tab1.js      # policy terms rows
    edit.js      # policy edit hydrate
  index.js       # barrel of short exports
```

### 3. Call style

```js
import { fillPlan, showErr, useShell } from '@/services/property_liability/burglary'
// or leaf:
import { useShell } from '@/services/property_liability/burglary/on'
```

Leaf exports **are** short. No long `DirectBook*` helpers. No dual aliases.

### 4. Do / don't

- **Do** put new helper in matching `burglary/` file (1–2 word filename + short export).
- **Don't** re-introduce `hydrateDirectBook*` / `DIRECT_BOOK_*` helper names.
- **Don't** move legacy `0121`–`0125` into `burglary/`.
- **Don't** grow `limits.js` / `plan.js` with one-off UI.

